{"root":{"data":{"id":"di2c7je3vao0","created":1777130565863,"text":"游戏概念与机制设想","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di2ck8uj1ow0","created":1777131561646,"text":"世界观与背景概念","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di2cs8ve1s80","created":1777132188611,"text":"思维细节\"一瞥\"","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di2csh789r40","created":1777132206741,"text":"是巨大悬浮碎石的天空，鲸鱼在云间游过？慢迁徙？","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di2cswppvpc0","created":1777132240511,"text":"是废弃空间站里，生锈仪表盘上最后一抹闪烁的微光？"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di2ct8g8p0o0","created":1777132266060,"text":"是雨水倒流的城市，人们撑着伞向天空行走？"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di2ctejzqk80","created":1777132279347,"text":"还是一只机械甲虫，驮着整座村庄在沙漠上缓慢迁徙？"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"di2cf6favig0","created":1777131164551,"text":"角色艺术概念","layout_mind_offset":{"x":709.999971787136,"y":159.99999364217143},"layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di2cfcoclq00","created":1777131178159,"text":"玩家在非战斗状态是一个可爱角色形象, 但在战斗状态切换为一个酷的风格, 但整体保持美术风格统一, 类似于埼玉的那种反差感","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di31ckk3e480","created":1777201487971,"text":"我角色有没有可能是一个人形态树?"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di31d6hkmww0","created":1777201535707,"text":"攀爬和地面行走都可以是藤曼或者树根在地理前行(潜行)"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di31e9uetbs0","created":1777201621378,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di31ea1gyg00","created":1777201621805,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di31efclrwg0","created":1777201633362,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di31eg6r1g00","created":1777201635185,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di31egozt000","created":1777201636288,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di31eh6sxuo0","created":1777201637365,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di31ehlzgxc0","created":1777201638283,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di31ei498s00","created":1777201639388,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di31ep3gchk0","created":1777201654577,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di31epz5f1c0","created":1777201656493,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di31er0d4io0","created":1777201658743,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di31esbn8zc0","created":1777201661602,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di31eshmge80","created":1777201661964,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di31esorz4w0","created":1777201662396,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di31esplaaw0","created":1777201662446,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di31esswl6o0","created":1777201662646,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di31esul4q80","created":1777201662749,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di31esxhty00","created":1777201662924,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di31eszg1go0","created":1777201663041,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di31et2adqg0","created":1777201663213,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di31et41mfc0","created":1777201663320,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di31et6flco0","created":1777201663464,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di31et7zpls0","created":1777201663558,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di31eta3ew80","created":1777201663685,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di31etbgcjs0","created":1777201663769,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di31etdrnuw0","created":1777201663908,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di31etevuhc0","created":1777201663975,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di31eth5x5c0","created":1777201664113,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di31etia22o0","created":1777201664180,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]}]}]}]}]}]}]}]}]}]}]}]}]}]}]}]}]}]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"di2chepwpq80","created":1777131339335,"text":"角色能力","expandState":"expand","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di2c834w6bk0","created":1777130608842,"text":"连招系统","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di2c8i7cdi80","created":1777130641642,"text":"将连击的每段设置为不同层级,每段动作美感和复杂程度提升, 但是能在每个层级内挑选一个动作, 达到随机衔接招式的目的","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"di2cbn6tj200","created":1777130887587,"text":"当敌人无法反抗时的斩击动作, (比如眩晕):按住常规x 攻击键的同时摇动手柄摇杆或者鼠标, 驱动动画疯狂斩击敌人","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"di2chm9yp880","created":1777131355785,"text":"技能树","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"di2chqybkrk0","created":1777131365965,"text":"让玩家在初始状态就拥有全部技能的使用权力, 但是随着玩家的偏好(例如使用某种技能最多), 那些技能会逐渐变强, 类似于通过训练逐渐掌握技能一样","layout":null,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[]}]}]}]},"template":"fish-bone","theme":"classic-compact","version":"1.4.43"}